00:15:02,475 --> 00:15:04,637
We'll also fix this by showing better screenshots that

320
00:15:04,758 --> 00:15:05,819
hint towards the genre.

321
00:15:06,339 --> 00:15:09,583
And we're going to be very trope conscious in our capsules

322
00:15:09,603 --> 00:15:12,325
because the capsules will hint as to what type of game this is.

323
00:15:12,986 --> 00:15:13,807
So let's take a look here.

324
00:15:14,862 --> 00:15:19,908
A lot of short descriptions describe the feeling, the emotions, what the graphics look like.

325
00:15:20,289 --> 00:15:24,454
Which is kind of a mistake because right to the side of the short descriptions are pictures.

