00:15:28,639 --> 00:15:29,100
And you'll notice

328
00:15:29,701 --> 00:15:31,702
They don't have to write that this is a spooky game.

329
00:15:31,823 --> 00:15:32,763
You just look at the screenshots.

330
00:15:32,783 --> 00:15:34,185
You're like, this is a spooky game.

331
00:15:34,225 --> 00:15:36,107
This is a horror-based in the woods game.

332
00:15:36,447 --> 00:15:39,089
So they can eliminate all those words from their description.

333
00:15:39,370 --> 00:15:40,511
They can focus on gameplay.

334
00:15:40,931 --> 00:15:43,534
So let your screenshots and your trailer

335
00:15:44,074 --> 00:15:48,298
use to describe the mood and kind of the feeling of the game.

336
00:15:48,659 --> 00:15:50,280
Don't waste words describing feeling.

337
00:15:50,620 --> 00:15:51,541
Screenshots will do that.

338
00:15:52,716 --> 00:15:56,639
Instead, I like to make my short descriptions verb-focused.

339
00:15:57,159 --> 00:15:59,381
Write down what you literally do in the game.

340
00:15:59,441 --> 00:16:00,602
What verbs do you use?

341
00:16:00,942 --> 00:16:03,725
Some helpful hints for writing your short description.

342
00:16:04,045 --> 00:16:06,347
These are kind of thought experiments I like to do.

343
00:16:06,827 --> 00:16:08,789
Say, write down all the verbs that happen

344
00:16:08,809 --> 00:16:10,170
when you push each of the face buttons

345
00:16:10,210 --> 00:16:11,831
if you were using a controller on this game.

346
00:16:12,071 --> 00:16:12,772
What are those verbs?

347
00:16:13,112 --> 00:16:15,033
Those verbs should appear in your short description.

348
00:16:15,654 --> 00:16:17,155
What happens if you die in the game?

349
00:16:17,596 --> 00:16:17,896
Do you...

350
00:16:19,837 --> 00:16:22,359
Do you die forever? Does the world reset?

351
00:16:22,919 --> 00:16:23,860
What happens when you die?

352
00:16:24,180 --> 00:16:25,901
That can really hint at the genre.

353
00:16:26,121 --> 00:16:27,803
Is it a roguelike where the world resets?

354
00:16:28,343 --> 00:16:29,944
Maybe. That really hints to it.

355
00:16:30,424 --> 00:16:31,865
Also describe how time works.

356
00:16:32,185 --> 00:16:33,967
Is it real time? Is it turn-based?

357
00:16:34,067 --> 00:16:35,388
Is there a real world clock?

358
00:16:36,328 --> 00:16:38,029
What is it? Is it like Animal Crossing where

359
00:16:38,610 --> 00:16:41,091
whatever day it is today is the time in Animal Crossing?

360
00:16:41,251 --> 00:16:42,953
All those things help hint to your genre.

361
00:16:43,233 --> 00:16:45,034
So describe these things in your short description.

362
00:16:46,086 --> 00:16:49,307
Here are some good examples. These are short descriptions that I really like.

