00:17:30,781 --> 00:17:32,943
is gonna be covered by those screenshots off to the side.

377
00:17:33,264 --> 00:17:34,805
So don't feel like your short description

378
00:17:34,865 --> 00:17:38,088
has to carry everything and have to enrapture

379
00:17:38,408 --> 00:17:39,369
all of it as your game.

380
00:17:39,750 --> 00:17:41,831
Your whole Steam page works around

381
00:17:41,891 --> 00:17:43,213
with the rest of your short description.

382
00:17:44,688 --> 00:17:48,633
So, let's talk about being crystal clear with your genre by getting better screenshots.

